{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/ruby/rails/nested-routes/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Kevin Ponce Blog","author":"Kevin Ponce"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2fa614cd-120d-5329-88b2-b6b4f3f23232","excerpt":"Rails 6.1 offically fixed large routes file!\nHere is an example of how to do this: config/routes.rb config/routes/api.rb","html":"<p>Rails 6.1 offically fixed large routes file!\nHere is an example of how to do this:</p>\n<h2>config/routes.rb</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\"><span class=\"token constant\">Rails</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>application<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>routes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>draw <span class=\"token keyword\">do</span>\n  draw<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token symbol\">:api</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  root <span class=\"token string\">'home#index'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>config/routes/api.rb</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ruby\"><pre class=\"language-ruby\"><code class=\"language-ruby\">namespace <span class=\"token symbol\">:api</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> defaults<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> format<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token symbol\">:json</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">do</span>\n  devise_for <span class=\"token symbol\">:users</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Rails nested routes","date":"March 15, 2021","description":"How to clean up rails routes","author":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/ruby/rails/nested-routes/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/python/send-gcode-through-serial-to-a-3d-printer-using-python/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Send gcode through serial to a 3D Printer using python","tags":["python"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/docker/Cheatsheet/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Docker Cheatsheet","tags":["docker"]}}}}}